This incredibly cute game puts kids in charge of their own musical productionâchoosing dancers, costumes and techno tracks, and choreographing moves using simple swipes and taps. Once the performance starts, the real fun begins: you can fling items at the stage, set off pyrotechnics and other cool effects and even cheer (or boo) your squad. Seeing the payoffâan awesome video you can shareâwill encourage players to jump right back in and start working on their next great show.
